          <p class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Common questions</h2>
          <div style="max-width:680px;margin-top:28px">
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>Does Pompelmi send files to a cloud API?<svg class="faq-chev" width="17" height="17" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary>
              <p class="faq-body">No. All scanning runs in-process inside your Node.js application. File bytes never leave your infrastructure — by design.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>Does it require a ClamAV daemon or sidecar?<svg class="faq-chev" width="17" height="17" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary>
              <p class="faq-body">No. The heuristic scanner and ZIP bomb protection run with zero external dependencies. ClamAV is available as an optional adapter for signature-based scanning.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>Can it detect ZIP bombs and nested archives?<svg class="faq-chev" width="17" height="17" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary>
              <p class="faq-body">Yes. Entry count, per-entry size, total decompressed bytes, and nesting depth are all enforced before the archive is fully extracted.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>What does Enterprise add for SOC 2 / HIPAA compliance?<svg class="faq-chev" width="17" height="17" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary>
